OL,3,COne in four fear having to turn off
OL,4,Cheating and hot water this winter `
OL,5,Csurvey
OL,7,FUp to a quarter of the UK population
OL,8,Fbelieve they could be forced to turn
OL,9,Foff their heating and hot water this
OL,10,Fwinter due to an expected rise in
OL,11,Fhousehold energy bills, research
OL,12,Fsuggests.
OL,14,FThe proportion who said they will need
OL,15,Fto take such drastic action increased
OL,16,Fto 31% for households with children
OL,17,Fand 39% for people on a low income, a
OL,18,Fsurvey by Citizens Advice found.
