OL,5,Csurvey
OL,7,FThe expected rise in bills comes after
OL,8,FChancellor Rachel Reeves announced
OL,9,Fthat the winter fuel allowance would
OL,10,Fno longer be universal, and only
OL,11,Fpensioners on means-tested benefits
OL,12,Fwould qualify for it this winter.
OL,14,FMinisters have launched a campaign to
OL,15,Furge those who still qualify to secure
OL,16,Fwinter fuel payments as Government
OL,17,Fplans are expected to strip away the
OL,18,Fenergy benefit from millions of
OL,19,Felderly people.
